{"tid":84182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普抨擊大陸竊取智財權 陸：他在陸申請不少商標","createTime":"2017-01-17T10:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T06:26:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b02a9ba728a1762497f4801ec402e5f0f868f3e2","tid":84182,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>川普抨擊大陸竊取智財權 陸：他在陸申請不少商標</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-01-17 13:33聯合報 <br />\n記者郭玫君╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人川普曾抨擊中國大陸大量竊取智慧財產權，大陸國家知識產權局副局長甘紹寧今天稱，川普在大陸申請過不少商標，這充分說明大陸的智慧財產權制度是「符合國際規則的」。<br />\n<br />\n他也說，中國願意與世界各國的同行之間加強知識產權的合作，共享發展的經驗；中國也反對「不切實際的指責」和「濫用知識產權實行貿易保護主義」。<br />\n<br />\n大陸國新辦今天舉行新聞發佈會，有記者問到，川普對中國大陸一系列政策中，有相當一部分是針對中國的知識產權政策，大陸對此有何評論？分析也指川普上台會利用知識產權等政策對中國發難，大陸有何應對立場和措施？<br />\n<br />\n甘紹寧表示，知識產權制度是各國通行的保護無形資產、激勵創新、鼓勵創新的法律制度。中國改革開放30多年來，走過了發達國家幾百年走過的道路，建立了完備的知識產權法律體系，與行政保護和司法保護優勢互補的、<strong>具有中國特色的法律保護制度安排</strong>，得到了世界各國的承認。<br />\n<br />\n他說，有報導說，川普先生在中國還申請過不少商標，這充分說明中國的知識產權制度是符合國際規則的。<br />\n<br />\n甘紹寧表示，中國作為一個發展中國家，實施知識產權制度的歷史不長，的確在工作中也存在一些問題，但是實行嚴格的知識產權保護，不僅僅是吸引外資、對外開放的需要、創新驅動發展的需要，也是經濟社會發展轉型升級的必然要求。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/4/2235087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F4%2F2235087&d=txGxP0W71hYQd4d9YDo6UnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=72b9cdeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/4/2235087</a>"},{"pid":"e5e1932cc1761463d4e0e46474394627641ef371","tid":84182,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"大陸真係幫唔落<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.worldjournal.com/4682064/article-&eacute;&brvbar;&not;&aelig;&iexcl;&para;&atilde;&aelig;&reg;&ordm;&egrave;&sup2;&aring;trump&aring;&aring;&frac14;&aring;&aelig;&uml;&eacute;&cent;&uml;&egrave;&iexcl;&auml;&cedil;&shy;&aring;/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F4682064%2Farticle-%C3%A9%C2%A6%C2%AC%C3%A6%C2%A1%C2%B6%C3%A3%C2%80%C2%81%C3%A6%C2%AE%C2%BA%C3%A8%C2%9F%C2%B2%C3%A5%C2%8A%C2%91trump%C3%A5%C2%90%C2%84%C3%A5%C2%BC%C2%8F%C3%A5%C2%95%C2%86%C3%A6%C2%A8%C2%99%C3%A9%C2%A2%C2%A8%C3%A8%C2%A1%C2%8C%C3%A4%C2%B8%C2%AD%C3%A5%C2%9C%C2%8B%2F&d=txGxP0W71hYQd4d9YDo6UnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b701b119\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.worldjournal.com/4682064/article-&eacute;&brvbar;&not;&aelig;&iexcl;&para;&atilde;&aelig;&reg;&ordm;&egrave;&sup2;&aring;trump&aring;&aring;&frac14;&aring;&aelig;&uml;&eacute;&cent;&uml;&egrave;&iexcl;&auml;&cedil;&shy;&aring;/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>這些年來中國有幾十個人試圖用川普(Trump)之名註冊商標，許多申請成功，因此有川普保險套、川普馬桶、川普殺蟲劑和川普油漆，雖然它們與當選美國總統的川普本人毫無關係。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2016122901232418_36695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F2016122901232418_36695.jpg&h=eda82781&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b19aed06c4f8f0bb8a41918fee49d5c4dfcafde9","tid":84182,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d586acab90aa775ca9b6d10618ec539767b19797","tid":84182,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T22:49:45.000Z","msg":"又變返個發展中國家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f38c5dc257afb6f44f8b6c0c2030e8133661d8","tid":84182,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}